Depletion (SSB relative to unfished SSB given current recruitment dynamics) for the first 10 projected years (a performance metrics function of class PM)

Depletion (SSB relative to unfished SSB given current recruitment dynamics) for the first 10 projected years (a performance metrics function of class PM)

D10

Arguments

MSE
An object of class MSE

Format

An object of class PM of length 1.

Value

a matrix with n Management procedures (MSE@nMP) and nsim (MSE@nsim) columns from MSE

Examples

loadABT()
#> ABT-MSE objects loaded
